categories: Category:Unidentified members of the Ohnaka Gang

nodes.text: This unnamed Weequay pirate was seen talking to Fong Do in Moshi Bar during the Clone Wars. He worked for Hondo Ohnaka's pirate gang. He was the first to notice that they were being spied on by Ahsoka Tano. He hinted to Do and they both pulled out their weapons at her. But before a fight could break out Ahsoka threw gold credits into the air as a distraction and the Jedi left the bar.
